Desserts
Sides



Dinners





                                Herb Roasted Chicken
                            

  Marinated roasted chicken seasoned with garden herbs, topped with a citrus garden herb sauce and garnished with a fresh cut lemon.  Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.
                            






                                Slow Roasted Turkey & Dressing
                            

                                Tender, hand-carved slices of turkey breast over our bread & celery dressing, topped with pan-roasted gravy and garnished with cranberry relish. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Bob Evans Broasted Chicken
                            

Our Broasted Chicken is marinated and hand-coated in a blend of our special spices.  Then we pressure fry it until it's the perfect combination of crispy on the outside and tender on the inside.   Served with choice of one Family-Size side and bread.
Limited Availability







                                Slow Roasted Pot Roast
                            

                                Our signature Pot Roast is slow-roasted for nine hours with fresh glazed carrots and grilled onions and drizzled with savory gravy. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Grilled Chicken Breasts
                            

                                Six marinated boneless chicken breasts with your choice of sauce. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Chicken & Noodles Deep Dish Dinner
                            

                                Our famous Chicken-N-Noodles made with slow-roasted chicken, ladled over a heaping pile of mashed potatoes and freshly made buttermilk biscuits. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Country Fried Steak
                            

                                Four pieces of tender beef lightly breaded and fried, then topped with creamy country gravy. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Pot Roast Sliders
                            

                                The handheld version of our signature slow-roasted beef served with freshly baked dinner rolls.
                            






                                Homestyle Fried Chicken Tenders
                            

                                12 Homestyle Fried Chicken tenders served with Bob Evans Wildfire BBQ Sauce, Honey Mustard or Ranch. Served with your choice of sides.  Serves 4
                            






                                Homestyle Fried Chicken
                            

                                Try our Homestyle Chicken, made with fresh, never frozen chicken and cooked so it's crispy-golden outside, juicy inside.    Served with choice of one Family-Size side and bread.
                            






                                Homestyle Fried Chicken Fillets
                            

                                Six Homestyle Fried Chicken boneless chicken breasts with your choice of sauce. Served with your choice of one or two savory sides and freshly baked bread. Serves 4
                            





Breakfasts





                                Farmers Breakfast
                            

                                Served with scrambled eggs, home fries, Bob Evans Sausage or hardwood-smoke bacon and your choice of one of the following: fruit crepes, hotcakes or French toast.  Serves 4
                            






                                Homestead Breakfast
                            

                                Named after our original farmhouse, this breakfast is a classic! Served with scrambled eggs, sausage gravy, the choice of Bob Evans Sausage, bacon or ham, and choice of a breakfast side and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Rise & Shine
                            

                                Our most popular breakfast. Served with scrambled eggs, the choice of Bob Evans Sausage, bacon or ham, choice of a breakfast side and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            





Salads & Soups





                                Wildfire Chicken Salad
                            

                                Fresh greens topped with your choice of chicken, tortilla strips, corn, tomatoes, scallions and cheddar cheese, served with Bob Evans Wildfire Ranch Dressing and your choice of freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Cranberry Pecan Chicken Salad
                            

                                Tender, slow-roasted chicken, bacon, sweet dried cranberries and bleu cheese tossed with fresh greens. Topped with honey-roasted pecans. Pairs well with our Sweet Italian dressing and served with your choice of savory side and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                Cobb Salad
                            

                                Tender chicken, bacon, a hard-boiled egg, grape tomatoes, scallions, cheddar and bleu cheese top crisp greens. Served with your choice of dressing, a savory side and freshly baked bread.  Serves 4
                            






                                The Green Goddess Salad
                            

                                Fresh romaine and spinach tossed with hardwood-smoked bacon, hard boiled egg, cucumbers and grilled chicken.  Served with our signature Green Goddess dressing.  Serves 4
                            






                                Chicken & Noodles
                            

                                Thick country-style egg noodles, slow-roasted, all-white-meat chicken and vegetables simmered in a rich broth. Serves 4
                            






                                Cheddar Baked Potato Soup
                            

                                Homestyle cuts of russet potatoes in a seasoned cheese sauce.  Serves 4
                            






                                Hearty Beef Vegetable Soup
                            

                                Tender beef slow-cooked in a tomato broth loaded with farm vegetables: carrots, corn, tomatoes, potatoes, celery and onions.
                            






                                Bob Evans Original Recipe Chili
                            

                                Packed with Bob Evans Sausage, fire roasted tomatoes, kidney beans, onions, hot sauce, and spices.  Serves 4
                            






                                Farm Festival Bean Soup
                            

                                Navy beans, smoked ham and diced onions in a seasoned light broth.  Serves 4
                            





Baked Breads





                                Freshly Baked Rolls
                            








                                Banana Nut Bread
                            








                                Freshly Baked Buttermilk Biscuits
                            








                                Cinnamon Coffee Cake
                            

                                Cinnamon Cake topped with streusel topping
                            






                                Lemonade Bread
                            







Desserts





                                Strawberry Supreme Pie
                            

                                It’s back! Rich cream cheese filling topped with a layer of fresh strawberries and whipped topping.
                            






                                Chocolate Peanut Butter Pie Topped with Reese's®
                            

                                Chocolate graham cracker crust with creamy peanut butter filling and topped with chocolate whipped topping and Reese's® Peanut Butter Cups.
                            






                                Double Crust Apple Pie
                            

                                Our Double-Crust Apple Pie is filled with crisp, tart Michigan apples and cinnamon and then baked to crispy, flaky perfection and drizzled with caramel. 
                            






                                Coconut Cream Pie   Whole
                            

                                This one's a classic! A layer of luscious coconut filling is topped with sweet, creamy whipped topping, then sprinkled with toasted coconut for an added touch of nostalgia.
                            






                                Lemon Supreme Pie
                            

                                Sweet cream cheese filling topped with tart lemon curd
                            





