                                Tomato Cucumber Salad
                            

                                Ripe fresh cut tomatoes, crisp diced cucumbers and sweet yellow onions tossed in a Champagne vinaigrette.
                            






                                Summer Herb Corn
                            

                                Sweet corn with diced fresh red and green peppers finished with a citrus garden herb sauce.
                            






