  Restaurant Management Benefits   
Growing with the best is an opportunity found only at Bob Evans Restaurants. With nearly 60 years in the family restaurant business, Bob Evans Restaurants has an excellent reputation for serving high quality food in a friendly atmosphere. We would welcome you as a part of our family to help us continue to build on this excellent foundation.
Geographical Flexibility
With geographical locations throughout nearly half of the United States, we work with you to try to get you to the area where you would like to build your career! Some geographical areas require relocation, if moving is required, we pay your moving costs!
Industry-Renown Training
We offer paid training program: previous restaurant knowledge and management experience is not required, but is considered a plus.
All restaurant management is certified in the National Restaurant Association’s ServSafe program and Applied Foodservice Sanitation Advanced training program throughout career.
Management Benefits:

