                                Classic Breakfast
                            

                                Bob Evans classic breakfast served with Scrambled Eggs, Hardwood-Smoked bacon or Bob Evans sausage links and buttermilk biscuits.  Serves 10.
                            






                                Western Egg Scramble
                            

                                Diced smoked ham, sautéed onions and green and red peppers scrambled together with shredded cheddar cheese. Served with homefries and buttermilk biscuits.  Serves 10.
                            






                                Border Egg Scramble
                            

                                Scrambled Eggs with Pepper Jack cheese. Served with Border Scramble mix, jalapenos and Sour cream. Homefries and Buttermilk Biscuits.  Serves 10.
                            






                                Vegetable Egg Scramble
                            

                                Scrambled Eggs loaded with broccoli, onions, mushrooms, red and green bell peppers and shredded cheddar cheese. Served with homefries and Buttermilk biscuits.  Serves 10.
                            






