Our Company



























Our Company
Our Company








Diversity
Bob Evans Farms has a long history of diversity and inclusion beginning with our founder, Bob Evans. Bob and his wife Jewell welcomed all people to their table, never turning away anyone, and we honor his legacy by continuing that tradition today.

Regardless of an individual’s place in the world, there is one universal truth that I’ve observed: despite our differences, there is a common desire to be respected and appreciated for who we are, individually.  As a representative of Bob Evans Farms, I hold myself personally accountable for fostering an environment where every employee can feel comfortable being themselves and for creating a culture that not only recognizes but also values the innovation that comes from diverse perspectives.
We know that diversity and inclusion make us a stronger company and allow us to better serve and build meaningful relationships with the guests, consumers and communities we serve every day. Bob Evans is and has always been about people – all people. Whether you’re in a restaurant, in one of our production plants, or in the corporate office, diversity and inclusion are everyone’s responsibility to perpetuate. I am proud of our work to this point and I am excited about our journey forward. Below you can read about our efforts toward ensuring equality through recruiting and hiring, philanthropy, and culture.
 
Our Diversity Statement
At Bob Evans we believe it’s not just about great food, it’s about great people. And we’re putting a tremendous amount of effort toward creating and sustaining a diverse and inclusive environment.
Recruiting & Hiring
We celebrate diversity and inclusion and make a conscious effort to seek out and develop the best employees from a variety of backgrounds and cultures. Bob Evans hires and promotes individuals based on their commitment to excellence without regard to race, ethnicity, national origin, religion, gender, age, disability, sexual orientation, gender identity or any other protected category or characteristic. We value all experiences and perspectives as part of our inclusive culture that fosters innovation and allows us to better understand and meet the needs of our consumers, our guests, their families and the communities we serve.
Culture
 
Our ongoing commitment to diversity and inclusion is proudly exemplified and supported through our Employee Resource Groups, which represent the many facets of diversity at Bob Evans.


Philanthropy
Our corporate philanthropic support of diverse organizations and causes is focused on building lasting relationships and having a positive impact on the community.
Suppliers
Finally, we are committed to engaging and mentoring diverse suppliers as part of our diversity and inclusion strategies thereby driving economic growth and sustainability in diverse markets and communities.
For us diversity and inclusion are not just programs or buzzwords. We know the importance of making them part of everything we do and recognize that it not only makes us a great place to work but allows us to treat our employees, suppliers and guests with respect and dignity.
 
   Proud coalition member of the 100,000 Jobs Mission
 
 
 


