			Company Description 


			Bob Evans Farms, Inc. operates as a restaurant and retail food products company. It produces and distributes pork sausage and a variety of complementary convenience food items under the Bob Evans and Owens brand names. It operates through the Bob Evans Restaurants and BEF Foods segments. The Bob Eva...
		


                Bob Evans Farms, Inc. operates as a restaurant and retail food products company. It produces and distributes pork sausage and a variety of complementary convenience food items under the Bob Evans and Owens brand names. It operates through the Bob Evans Restaurants and BEF Foods segments. The Bob Evans Restaurants segment includes rise & shine breakfast, sausage gravy 'n biscuits, turkey and dressing, and knife and fork sandwiches. The BEF Foods segment offers a variety of home-style food products to retail and foodservice customers. The company was founded by Bob Evans in 1946 and is headquartered in New Albany, OH.
            




