            Additional Information
        


                BBB is in the process of further communicating with the companies involved and updating BBB Business Profiles as the result of Jan. 24, 2017 news that Bob Evans Farms, Inc. announced agreements for the sale of Bob Evans Restaurants and the purchase o...
            



BBB is in the process of further communicating with the companies involved and updating BBB Business Profiles as the result of Jan. 24, 2017 news that Bob Evans Farms, Inc. announced agreements for the sale of Bob Evans Restaurants and the purchase of Pineland Farms Potato Company. Meanwhile, additional information published on the Bob Evans website available at this link: http://investors.bobevans.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=1008982 




