	Bob Evans Farms, Inc. is a publically traded food products company listed on the NASDAQ exchange under the ticker symbol BOBE. The company is a leading producer and distributor of refrigerated potato, pasta and vegetable-based side dishes, pork sausage, and a variety of refrigerated and frozen convenience food items under the Bob Evans and Owens brand names.

